===================================================================== Half-Life Map Spec Sheet ===================================================================== 

------General Information-------------------------------------------- 

Title : Rennes - Commercial Center "Colombia"

 Release : Version 1 

Date : 13th February 2004 

Filename : de_rennes_v1.bsp 

Author : Quezako 

Email Address : quezako@hotmail.com 

Home page : www.quezako.com 

Description : A real Commercial Center called "Colombia" in Rennes, France. 

Previous Maps : Some stupid maps for Quake3 (fort_boyard, pinball, glass_maze...), : Same Rennes map for ICS, a SOF2 mod. 

Credits/Thanks : Thanks to my Britanny's friends for beta-testing and ideas. : Kim, Deeway, Praka, MC_RaT, BZH-Clan and NicoSoft guys and all the others I forgot.  

------Play Information----------------------------------------------- 

Counter-Strike : Bomb/Defusion - 48 starts defined. (yes it's huge ;)) 

The bomb targets are indicated with site A and B tags. Notes: The map is the exact copy of the commercial center. I took a picture of the emergency evacuation map and used it as a template. I also took a lot of pictures of the center itself for dimensions and textures purpose. The v2 will be more detailed and with less reflection/tiny brushes problems. here is a lot of reflections. If this affects your machine, you can set mat_specular to 0 in the console (take several seconds).

  ------Map Information------------------------------------------------ 

New Textures : 12 (+ 24 shop logos). New Sounds : None (will be some for v2). 

------Construction---------------------------------------------------

  Base : from scratch (evacuation map) Editor(s) used : Hammer 4.0 build 3008 Compile Machine : P4 3Ghz Compile time : 15 mins 

------Map Instructions----------------------------------------------- 

Extract "maps" and "materials" directories in "cstrike"

  ------Additional Info------------------------------------------------ 

You may contact me if you want to create a map pack, a mod or other maps. ;)

  ------Copyright-Permissions------------------------------------------ 

Authors MAY NOT use this level as a base to build additional levels. You MUST NOT distribute this level UNLESS you INCLUDE THIS FILE WITH NO MODIFICATIONS!!!. If you don't co-operate, then DON'T DISTRIBUTE IT IN ANY FORM!!. This BSP may be distributed ONLY over the Internet and/or BBS systems. You are NOT authorized to put this BSP on any CD or distribute it in any way without my permission.
